OL,6,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,7,Fsome readers may find distressing
OL,9,FAn armed mob who killed a DPD worker
OL,10,Fwhile he was making deliveries has
OL,11,Fbeen convicted.
OL,13,FAurman Singh was part of a two-man
OL,14,Fcrew working in Shrewsbury.
