OL,3,CArmed mob convicted of horror killing
OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FMasked thugs brutally ambushed him in
OL,7,Fa chilling attack which lasted just
OL,8,F"seconds".JThe 23-year-old was
OL,9,Fslaughtered with weapons including a
OL,10,F3.5-lb axe, golf club, wooden stave,
OL,11,Fmetal bar, hockey stick, shovel, knife
OL,12,Fand cricket bat.
OL,14,FTerrified parents quickly ushered
OL,15,Ftheir children inside their homes as
OL,16,Fthey watched the armed men invade
OL,17,Ftheir street.
