OL,6,FAurman's panicked workmate instantly
OL,7,Frushed away from the street, shouting
OL,8,Fat his friend to run for his life
OL,9,Fafter spotting the weapon-wielding
OL,10,Fkillers hunting down his colleague.
OL,12,FBut Aurman only managed to sprint a
OL,13,Ffew yards before collapsing to the
OL,14,Fground and falling victim to a vicious
OL,15,Fonslaught. He was left for dead.
OL,17,FHis killers made a quick bid for
OL,18,Ffreedom, fleeing in the two cars they
OL,19,Fhad arrived in and taking some of
OL,20,Ftheir weapons with them.
