OL,6,FA video of the axe and wooden stave
OL,7,Fwas filmed moments after they got back
OL,8,Finto the vehicles.
OL,10,FA total of five men denied murdering
OL,11,FAurman, from Smethwick, and stood
OL,12,Ftrial at Stafford Crown Court.
OL,14,FJurors convicted four of them of
OL,15,Fmurder on Thursday, 28 March.
OL,17,FThey now face life sentences for their
OL,18,Fhorrific execution in Berwick Avenue,
OL,19,FShrewsbury, on 21 August last year.
