OL,6,FA trial which started in February at
OL,7,FStafford Crown Court heard how police
OL,8,Fpieced together the movements of the
OL,9,Fkillers and their victim in the lead-
OL,10,Fup to the murder.
OL,12,FFootage from CCTV captured Aurman
OL,13,Fwalking into DPD's depot in Stoke-on-
OL,14,FTrent just after 6.52am.
OL,16,FJust before 7.15am, he was seen behind
OL,17,Fthe DPD van before it was to be loaded
OL,18,Fwith deliveries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/14
