OL,3,CArmed mob convicted of horror killing
OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FDefendant Sukhmandeep Singh - who was
OL,7,Fnot present during the deadly attack
OL,8,Fbut described as the 'inside man'
OL,9,Foffering up information on the
OL,10,Fvictim's whereabouts - was seen using
OL,11,Fa mobile phone.
OL,13,FHe was said to have taken a picture of
OL,14,Fthe DPD van and sent it to his
OL,15,Faccomplices, jurors heard.
OL,17,FAn Audi - which carried the convicted
OL,18,Fkillers to the scene - and the
OL,19,FMercedes, were captured in Shaw Road,
OL,20,FTipton, just before 9.50am.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
