OL,6,FThe boot of the Mercedes was seen to
OL,7,Fbe open while several men stood around
OL,8,Fit.
OL,10,FBoth cars then travelled to get fuel
OL,11,Ffrom Esso, in Dudley Port, Tipton,
OL,12,Fbefore stopping in the car park
OL,13,Foutside Castlefields Community Hub, in
OL,14,FShrewsbury.
OL,16,FFootage captured the Mercedes arriving
OL,17,Ffirst, with the four wanted men
OL,18,Fpopping into a nearby Morrisons Daily.
