OL,3,CArmed mob convicted of horror killing
OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FThey walked over to the Audi once it
OL,7,Farrived, with all the men "standing
OL,8,Ftogether" for "several minutes" before
OL,9,Fleaving.
OL,11,FEmpty sandwich packets were later
OL,12,Fdiscovered by police in the Audi.
OL,14,FThe cars were recorded arriving in
OL,15,FCoton Mount, Shrewsbury, and seen to
OL,16,Fbe "waiting" at 12.06pm.
OL,18,FJurors heard how the DPD van drove
OL,19,Falong that same street just after 1pm,
OL,20,Fwith both cars following it as it
OL,21,Ftravelled up Berwick Avenue.
