OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FFootage showed unsuspecting Aurman on
OL,7,Fhis phone in the front passenger seat
OL,8,Fof the parked van as his colleague
OL,9,Fmade a delivery.
OL,11,FCameras in nearby Round Hill Green
OL,12,Fshowed Aurman's colleague running from
OL,13,Fthe scene at 1.05pm.
OL,15,FIt was at this point that Aurman's
OL,16,Ffate was sealed and he was ambushed by
OL,17,Fhis killers.
