OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FThe armed thugs were seen running back
OL,7,Fto the Audi and Mercedes, with both
OL,8,Fvehicles fleeing "at speed" just one
OL,9,Fminute later.
OL,11,FAs the mob left the spot, Aurman's
OL,12,F"hesitant" colleague ducked behind a
OL,13,Fblack vehicle as he tried to make his
OL,14,Fway back to the DPD van.
OL,16,FHe discovered Aurman's severely
OL,17,Fwounded body on the ground.
