OL,6,FAn unmarked police vehicle managed to
OL,7,Flocate the Audi at about 2.20pm as it
OL,8,Fescaped from Shrewsbury to the Black
OL,9,FCountry.
OL,11,FA police helicopter then captured the
OL,12,FAudi stopping in Amphlett Croft, in
OL,13,FTipton, 20 minutes later.
OL,15,FDefendant Arshdeep Singh was seen
OL,16,F"rummaging" in the boot of the car
OL,17,Fbefore dumping the axe in a wheelie
OL,18,Fbin.
