OL,4,Cof DPD worker
OL,6,FOfficers attempted to bring the Audi
OL,7,Fto a stop as it made its getaway by
OL,8,Fdeploying a stinger but the driver
OL,9,Fmanoeuvred around it.
OL,11,FThe Audi finally came to a stop,
OL,12,Fsurrounded by police and dogs.
OL,14,FThe four occupants of the Audi dropped
OL,15,Fto the floor before they were
OL,16,Fhandcuffed.
OL,18,FAll five men - who have been remanded
OL,19,Fin custody - will be sentenced at a
OL,20,Fdate to be fixed.
